{"tid":1463833,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"認真，要解散機場集會真係好簡單","createTime":"2019-08-13T13:52:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T14:02:50.000Z","uid":163734,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d8ef1a17b00c2d35ee632d55f1b7cfefe0d61456","tid":1463833,"uid":163734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:52:19.000Z","msg":"一直派人喺入面撩事鬥非<br />\n屌鳩遊客同香港人就okay<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n麻煩記住初衷：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">機場集會係向外國人宣傳香港而家發生緊咩事<br />\nCall to action 俾佢地知點樣幫我地</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n人多起上來自己唔洗大家去攔住人都可以令AA做野。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n＃不割蓆，不督灰<br />\n＃五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n＃以眼還眼"},{"pid":"5ec844d7dbef4431d2efd915edc9a7260b6285b5","tid":1463833,"uid":163734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:52:51.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"4fe8f7a6ddede1940c60e2dec27c08eaec6e7138","tid":1463833,"uid":163734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:53:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de91ee9b07c1f5c12edb68e39ff60f1fdd874477","tid":1463833,"uid":163734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:53:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31260dd238d34fd3aca6c9a32e13cc34f7186224","tid":1463833,"uid":163734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:53:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88042e7afe84639d599047dda2552f638fadc536","tid":1463833,"uid":163734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:53:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd604ea68d9a9e09427999add4073e33f5324b04","tid":1463833,"uid":68471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:53:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">塞旅客一定要塞如果唔係出機場做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n塞嘅話，留返一個counter/閘口出黎，放一條極細既路出黎，由佢地排條好長既隊，排都排一兩粒鐘。其他路block Q曬，咁你就人道了無位比人入了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n圍師必缺，你唔使塞死，已經塞死。</span>"},{"pid":"50be9baf42dac3c559ff53d39402fece57c9c9b7","tid":1463833,"uid":279111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:56:41.000Z","msg":"「破解機場民意論」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1463130\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1463130</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n不解釋了，如果一直只宣傳唔做任何行動，係唔會有效，文宣加癱瘓先係正路"},{"pid":"c9eba067a89f8916bbd8484a7abafef74a535d6a","tid":1463833,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:02:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">卧底做緊架啦</span></span>"},{"pid":"6c22f440abb8d2a009258d235d8a6639572c3fd9","tid":1463833,"uid":134206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:02:50.000Z","msg":"push"}]}